\id EPH EFE - TEKE - TYEE
\h EFEDZE
\toc3 Efe
\toc2 Efedze
\toc1 MUKAANA A POOLE KUNDAA BASI EFEDZE
\mt2 Mukaana a Poole Kundaa basi
\mt1 Efedze
\imt1 OSOMO
\ip Wu me mukaana wu ósono Poole kundaa bangaa a kana ba bali ku Efedze. Lo nde ka ásono mukaana wu yini a mu nkooro a bo o, mu kuulu, mu mikaana milagha mi mikulu, ka básono kwumu yi a «Efedze» mu etsulu kii nsomo o. Odzyi osuo ti Poole ásono mukaana wu kundaa banga-a-kana baba mabvulu malagha mama ku etsulu e nsie kii Adzi, mpaala bo bamana otaŋa nde, bagwa nde kundaa banganda. Nde ásono mukaana wu mu matala ma áli nde mu boloko ku Rome.
\ip Efedze líli bvulu li libvulu mupfunu ŋa kara li mabvulu mwohono mama empu kii Rome ma máli ku Adzi. Baara balagha ŋa kara li baara ba bákakala oko báli minta-nkaala. Bo bátwu nzaami a bo wu a nkwumu Aretemise nzo yi a nkara bubwe. Basi-Rome baakata nde mu nkwumu yi a Dyane. Aretemise áli etyeghe mu efaana kii mukaha. Bo bákagye mu nzo yi a nkara mbwe oyo mu okayisamana kye. Baara bwohono baba oko bákasa kana mu etyeghe ekye, maha ba-Dzwife ya bakriste. Mu matala ma obvughuru Poole ku Efedze mu midzye mi nde mimi myele, nde áluo ba-Dzwife baba oko mu etsughu kii Sabate. Ŋa mbihi, nde abvughuru mu kuulu nde ka ákughu ogyili oko o, lo nde ályele bo ti nde faana obvughuru. Mu matala ma abvughuru nde mu midzye mimi mitere, nde ási bamvulu batere mu okaluo baara matala mwohono (\xt Big 19–20\xt*).
\ip Mandagha ma me ma ookasuo Poole munsa mukaana wu: Nzaami aasuo bihi mandagha ma básweghe ma akuru nde mu bubwe bu nde. Mbaala ti, nde sa abvughu bilogho byehene bibi ku mayulu, ya bi bili ŋa nsie mpaala Yiisu akala Mfumu. Nde ábwehe ti bakriste bafaana ogwihini ya okala ti anga bandughu mu kana. Ka bafaana olyele o ti wu mu-Dzwife, wunii ka li mu-Dzwife o. Mutaara a bo li yini a mumõ, me Satana. Mu obo, bo bafaana okasamana ŋa emõ mpaala Satana anyaã okala a litumu ŋa yulu a bo. Poole áfirilyele bunu a bo baghala afaana okala ya mukala a nde, bunu a bo baana bafaana ogwolo bataara ba bo, bunu a bo bankana bafaana okagwolo bamfumu ba bo. Nde ályele ti banga-a-kana bafaana okala bumõ ya Kriste.
\ib
\iot Bu me bu baakakaba mukaana wu:
\io1 1) Mamboro (\xt 1.1-2\xt*)
\io1 2) Kriste seme bihi ya Mufulu a Ngili (\xt 1.3–3.21\xt*)
\io1 3) Litswe likala a bumweẽ bu bunyaghara emõ ya Kriste (\xt 4.1–6.20\xt*)
\io1 4) Mamboro mama masini (\xt 6.21-24\xt*).
\c 1
\s1 Mamboro
\p 
\v 1 Me Poole, ntumu a Yiisu-Kriste mu waa li Nzaami, nsono mukaana wu kundaa baba ngili ba bali ku bvulu lili Efedze, ba baakasa kana mu Yiisu-Kriste:
\v 2 Nyaã bwehe ya edzuunu bi bifi kundaa Nzaami Taara a bihi ya kundaa Mfumu Yiisu-Kriste bikala ya be!
\s1 Liseme lili mukughu mu Kriste
\p 
\v 3 Masyighi kundaa Nzaami, Taara a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste, nde wu aaseme bihi mu Kriste mu liseme lwohono lili mufulu mu mayulu.
\v 4 Mu nde, Nzaami ásuolo bihi nsomo nde agyighili nsie, mpaala bihi likala baba ngili, ba bagwene a epfwumu ŋa busu bu nde. Mu dzyi li nde, Nzaami
\v 5 átswamagwolo munkaana mu osa ti bihi likala baana ba nde mu Yiisu-Kriste, ti bwunu a bu oli waa li nde li libwe,
\v 6 mu kuulu bihi lisyighi nsia a bwehe bu nde, bwehe bu aapfwaha nde bihi mu mwana a nde wu a dzyi.
\p 
\v 7 Mu makili ma Yiisu, Nzaami aakwulu bihi, nde aasi masumu ma bihi kolokolo, ti bwunu a bu oli busini bu bwehe bu nde.
\v 8 Nzaami aapfwaha bihi bo kunsa bunsughu bwohono ya mayele mwohono.
\v 9 Nde aasuo bihi mansweghe ma waa li nde, bitsimi bi bibwe bi átswama okuru nde mu Kriste,
\v 10 mu okuhu bye ŋa ookughu matala mpaala abvughu byehene kunsa litumu li Kriste, byehene bi bili mu mayulu ya bi bili ŋa nsie.
\p 
\v 11 Mu Kriste bihi si liibagha kaba lili pfa, bihi ba básuolo nsomo ti bwunu a bu oli bitsimi bi ókuru munde wu aakagyighili mandagha mwohono ti bwunu a bu oli munkaana a waa li nde,
\v 12 mpaala lisyighi nsia a nde, bihi ba lítswama osa emiini e bihi mu Kriste.
\p 
\v 13 Mu nde, behe si bu ligyughu mandagha mama ngaŋma, nsia yi mbwe yi a obvwughu o be, mu nde si be liisi kana ya baasi be elyimi kii Mufulu a Ngili wu básiini a be.
\v 14 Mufulu munde li kaba lili nsomo mu pfa li liibagha bihi. Bihi sa libagha lo mu matala ma baakwulu bihi kuu mukughu, mpaala bihi lisyighi nsia a nde.
\s1 Osamana o Poole
\p 
\v 15 Me mu obo mehe-si, bu aangyughu bu bali mu okabili mu kana li be mu Mfumu Yiisu ya mu dzyi li lili a be mu baba ngili bwohono,
\v 16 me ndi mu okabvurulu matuono mu be matala mwohono. Ya me aakansamana mu be.
\v 17 Nyaã Nzaami a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste, Taara wu a nsia, agwa be mufulu wu a bunsughu ya wu aakasuo mandagha mama ensweghe, wu aasa ti be lisoolo nde.
\v 18 Nyaã Nzaami abaha mikolo mi be mu obaghala ya osoolo nki emiini ki bákuru mu mbili yi áti nde be, nki busini bubu nsia a pfa li nde ŋa kara li baba ngili,
\v 19 ya nki bunene bu lileene nde aasuo kundaa bihi ba liikasa kana, lileene lilo li aasuo nde ya mpini yohono.
\p 
\v 20 Nde aasuo lileene lilo bu aasiili Kriste ŋa kara li ba bákpi ya aabwihi nde nsini ŋa kwogho-a-kwogho e nde mu mayulu.
\v 21 Mu obo, Kriste li ŋa yulu a bimfumu byehene, litumu lwohono, lileene lwohono, empu kyehene ya nswe nkwumu yi bakughu otaŋana, ka yini a mu matala ma o, lo ya mu matala ma maagya si.
\v 22 \qt Nzaami aasuhu byehene ku nsie a myili mi Kriste\qt*, ya nde aatwulu nde mu okala mutswi ŋa yulu a byehene, mutswi a libwunu li Nzaami,
\v 23 li lili nyuru a nde, mukughu wu a munde wu aakaluhu byehene mu baara bwohono.
\c 2
\s1 Obvughu mu bwehe
\p 
\v 1 Lo be, be áli líipki mu nkooro a bibili bi be ya masumu ma be.
\v 2 Be áli líikanama bipfu bi baara ba nsie yi, be líikanama litumu li mfumu a mifulu mi mili mu engie-a-ngie. Me mufulu munde li mu okasala mu matala ma mu ba baakabihi litumu li Nzaami.
\v 3 Bihi bwohono si líili ti anga bo ya mu nsi-nkulu líikabuludzyara bwunu a bu oli dzyi li embwuru e bihi, mu okabulugyighili mi odzyi nyuru ya bitsimi bi bihi. Mu nzya-nzyara a bihi, bihi líili baara baala nkehe a Nzaami yífaana obwa mu bihi ti anga mu babake.
\v 4 Lo Nzaami alwulu mu nyiĩ, ya mu nkooro a dzyi li linene li adzyi nde bihi,
\v 5 bihi baala áli líikpi mu nkooro a masumu ma bihi, nde aabvurulu bihi baba mweẽ emõ ya Kriste. Me mu bwehe bu Nzaami be liibvwughu.
\v 6 Nde aasiili bihi mu lipfu ya aabwihi bihi nsini mu mayulu emõ ya Yiisu-Kriste,
\v 7 mu osuo mu matala ma maagya, busini bu bwehe bu nde bu bubvulu olagha, mu bubwe bu nde kundaa bihi mu Yiisu-Kriste.
\p 
\v 8 Mu kuulu, me mu bwehe baabvwuhu be, mu nzili a kana. Obvwughu oko ka ofi kundaa beme o, ko oli ekaba e Nzaami.
\v 9 Ka oli mu nkooro a bigyighili o, mpaala mbwuru si mumõ anyaã okala a ligwagha.
\v 10 Mu kuulu bihi lili baara ba ógyighili Nzaami. Nde áagyighili bihi mu Yiisu-Kriste mpaala likala a bigyighili bi bibwe, bigyighili bi átswama okuru nde, buulu bihi lisalala bye.
\s1 Ba-Dzwife ya baala ka bali ba-Dzwife o bali mbwuru mumõ mu Kriste
\p 
\v 11 Mu obo, liikalibili mweẽ mu ndagha yi: Mu nsi-nkulu be líili baala ka bali ba-Dzwife o mu musunu, bákalyele be ti ba bágwene osomo nzo a mbaa kundaa ba baakatsimi ti bo básomo nzo a mbaa, lo básomo nzo a mbaa mu manyuru ma bo ya mu myaã mi baara.
\v 12 Mu matala mamo be ka líli a Kriste o, be líili banzyi mu nsie a Isarayele, banzyi mu ogwihini ku misiini, ba bagwene a emiini ya ba bagwene a Nzaami mu nsie.
\v 13 Lo mu matala ma, mu Yiisu-Kriste, be baala mu nsi-nkulu líili la, be ayi be-bele mu makili ma Kriste.
\p 
\v 14 Mu kuulu me nde li edzuunu e bihi, nde wu aasi kuulu ti Ba-dzwife ya baala ka bali Ba-dzwife o bakala ekaana emõ. Bu aagwi nyuru a nde, nde aatsala ebagha kii eekakabala bo, ya ki eekalo etaara ŋa kara li bo.
\v 15 Nde aasyehe Mikyene ekulu emõ ya mikele ya litumu li mye, mpaala mu ndeme, nde agyighili mu bo bansa buolo, mbwuru mutsyini wu munyaghara, mu osa edzuunu,
\v 16 ya mu osa ogwihini ŋa kara li bansa buolo ya Nzaami mu nyuru nga-mõ mu kuruwa, bu amana mbele.
\v 17 Nde aayagwa nsia, ti anga nsia yi mbwe, edzuunu kundaa be ba líli la, ya edzuunu kundaa ba báli be-bele.
\v 18 Buulu mu nde, bihi bansa buolo lili a muswa mu osomo ŋa oli Taara mu Mufulu nga-mumõ.
\p 
\v 19 Mu obo, be ka lifirisyili banzyi o, ngu okala baara ba baafi mu mansie makimi. Lo be ayi basi nsie emõ ya baba ngili, baara baba dzumu li Nzaami.
\v 20 Be baatwu be ŋa yulu a bitsini bi bibagha bi nzo bi bili bantumu ya mibighili, ya Yiisu-Kriste ndeme li limeẽ lili ŋa mutswunu li liikakwara nzo .
\v 21 Me mu nde nzo yohono yiigwama ya yiitemene mu okala nzo a nzaami yi a ngili mu Mfumu.
\v 22 Mu nde behe si bátwu be emõ mu okala nzo yi ookakala Nzaami mu Mufulu.
\c 3
\s1 Mansweghe ma Kriste
\p 
\v 1 Mu ndagha oyo, me Poole ndi mbwuru a boloko mu esala e Yiisu-Kriste mu nkooro a be, baala ka lili ba-Dzwife o...
\v 2 Kala ti be líigyughu, bwunu a bu oli esala e bwehe bu Nzaami ki bágwi me mu nkooro a be.
\v 3 Mu limono baasuo me mansweghe ma Nzaami, ti bwunu a bu aansono me be mo mapfi-mapfi mu mukaana wu.
\v 4 Bu litaã mukaana wu, be likughu obaghala mayele ma ndi a me mu mansweghe ma Kriste.
\v 5 Mansweghe mamo ka básuo mo kundaa baana ba baara mu biseene bibike o ti anga bu baasuo mo mu matala ma mu Mufulu kundaa bantumu ba nde baba ngili ya mibighili:
\v 6 Mu osoolo ti baala ka bali ba-Dzwife o bali a pfa limõ lyini lilo, bali nyuru mõ gyini oyo, bali mu misiini myini mimye, mu Yiisu-Kriste mu nsia yi mbwe.
\v 7 Mu nkooro a Nsia yi Mbwe oyo me ayi musala, ti bwunu a bu oli ekaba e bwehe bu Nzaami bu baagwi kundaa me, mu nzili a bwehe bu nde.
\p 
\v 8 Kundaa me, me wu mbvulu busala mu mupfunu ŋa kara li baba ngili bwohono, baagwi me bwehe bubo buu otsala kundaa baala ka bali ba-Dzwife o muyighi a busini bu Kriste, ti anga nsia yi mbwe,
\v 9 ya mu osuo ŋa tse-tse kundaa baara bwohono omoŋono o mansweghe ma Nzaami, nde wu áagyighili bilogho byehene, ábunu mansweghe mamo obaana ku ebaana.
\v 10 Mpaala mu nzili a libwunu li Nzaami, bamfumu ya ba baakatumu mu mayulu basoolo bunsughu bu Nzaami bubu bifa-bifa,
\v 11 ti bwunu a bu aagyighili nde, mu Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste, bitsimi bi ákuru nde mu mibvu ya mibvu.
\v 12 Mu Yiisu-Kriste, ya mu kana li bihi mu nde, bihi lili a emiini ki ekughu mu obehene ya Nzaami mu kana.
\v 13 Mu obo me nduomo be mu onyaã otsili bukyini mu nkooro a mpara yi ndi mu okamono me mu be. Mpara oyo yili nsia a be.
\s1 Nyaã Kriste akala mu mikolo mi be
\p 
\v 14 Me mu obo me nkunu mabuo ŋa nkulu a Taara.
\v 15 Me nde aakagwa nkwumu kundaa nswe dzumu li lili ku yulu ya ŋa nsie.
\v 16 Mpaala mu busini bu nsia a nde, agwa be mpini ya lileene mu Mufulu a nde, mu nkooro a ndaana a mikolo mi be.
\v 17 Nyaã Kriste akala munsa mikolo mi be mu kana, ya be limyehe midza ya likala ba bágwama mu dzyi,
\v 18 mpaala emõ ya baba ngili bwohono be lileene obaghala bunene, bula, muyighi, mutele,
\v 19 ya dzyi li Kriste li liluru ligyahaba lwohono. Mu obo be liilwulu mu busini bu Nzaami bwohono.
\p 
\v 20 Kundaa munde wu kughu ogyighili ku obvulu mi liikaluomo ya mi liikatsimi bihi mu lileene li nde li liikasala mu bihi,
\v 21 kundaa nde nsia munsa libwunu li Nzaami ya mu Yiisu-Kriste, mu biseene byehene, mu mibvu ya mibvu. \qt Aamene!\qt*
\c 4
\s1 Otwu nyuru a Kriste mu bumõ ya mu dzyi
\p 
\v 1 Mu obo, me ngwi be mpama, me wu ndi mu boloko mu kuulu me aakansalala Mfumu, mu okala a nzya-nzyara yi faana ya mbili yi líkihi be,
\v 2 kunsa okughulu kwohono ya mu edzuunu, ya okakuru mukolo mu okebe. Mu dzyi, liikakuru mukolo mu nzya-nzyara a babake be a be,
\v 3 bu lisi makpa mu okakebe bumõ bu ookagwa Mufulu mu munama wu edzuunu.
\p 
\v 4 Oli a nyuru yini a mõ ya Mufulu yini a mumõ, bumõ si Nzaami áti be mbili mu emiini yini a emõ.
\q1 
\v 5 Oli a Mfumu yini a mumõ, kana yini a limõ, liboghoro yini a limõ,
\q1 
\v 6 Nzaami yini a mumõ ya Taara a bwohono,
\q1 wu aakatumu bwohono, wu aakasala mu bwohono, ya wu li mu bwohono.
\m 
\v 7 Lo kundaa nswe mbwuru mu bihi, baagwi bwehe, ti bwunu a bu oli eteese ki ekaba e Kriste.
\v 8 Me mu obo bályele ti:
\q1 \qt Ŋa ákumu nde ku yulu,\qt*
\q1 \qt nde ábiri baara ba boloko, \qt*
\q1 \qt nde ágwi baara bikaba.\qt*
\m 
\v 9 \qt Nde ákumu!\qt* Bunu odzyi olyele, nsomo nde akumu, nde átswama okumunu ku nsini a nsie?
\v 10 Munde wu aakumunu, me wuunu munde si aakumu ku nkara a mayulu mwohono, mpaala aluhu bilogho byehene.
\p 
\v 11 Ya nde aasi kuulu ti, bana bakala bantumu, babamõ mibighili, babake ba baakatsala nsia yi mbwe, ya babake minkaala bibuolo ya baluo.
\v 12 Nde aasi obo mu kuulu baba ngili bakala ba bakughu mu osala esala kii otwu nyuru a Kriste,
\v 13 tee mu matala ma liito bihi bwohono mu bumõ bu kana ya ligyahaba li Mwana a Nzaami, ya bihi sa likala kara a mukughu ti anga Kriste wu li mukughu.
\v 14 Mu obo, bihi ka lifirikala bike-bike o, ba ookanyihi mampo ma madza ya ba ookabiri bifulu bibi maluo. Bihi ka lifirikihi o ti bakaŋene ya ba bakadzihibi bihi mu mpya ya mayele baara ma mabi.
\v 15 Lo bu liikalyele ngaŋma munsa dzyi, bihi lifaana okulu mu mandagha mwohono mu Kriste, nde wu li mutswi.
\v 16 Me mu nde, binama bi nyuru byehe bibvuŋunu ebini emõ mu libaha li misunu ya mikaã. Mu obo, ŋa okasala nswe enama bwunu a bu ofaana, nyuru yohono yiikakulu mu dzyi.
\s1 Mbwuru wu mukulu ya mbwuru wu munyaghara
\p 
\v 17 Mu obo, ndagha yi ndyele me ya yinsuo me be bumpughulu mu Mfumu me yi: Ka lifirikala a nzya-nzyara a baara ba bagwene osoolo Nzaami o, baala bitsimi bi bo yini a mu mandagha ma magwene a mupfunu.
\v 18 Mayele ma bo mali kunsa mpyibi, ya bo bali banzyi mu bumweẽ bu Nzaami, mu nkooro a nzi-nzimini yi li mu bo ya mu nkooro a mikolo ngyi mi bo.
\v 19 Bo ka baafirikamono bupfiri o, bo áyi batyeghe manyuru ma bo mu mandagha mama enkwunu, bo baakagyighili mandagha mama osuŋumu mama mawa-mawa.
\p 
\v 20 Lo be, ka obo be liisoolo Kriste o,
\v 21 kala ti me nde be liigyughu ya baaluo be, ti bwunu a bu oli engaŋma ki eli mu Yiisu.
\v 22 Lo be lifaana odzwulu embwuru e be ki ekulu ki efaana ya nzya-nzyara a be yi nkulu, ya ki eekabyihi kyeme mu manzala ma kye mama mpya.
\v 23 Be lifaana okighiri mu mufulu mu mayele ma be
\v 24 ya olaha embwuru ki enyaghara, ki baagyighili mu efa kii Nzaami, munsa bunsumu ya bungili bu buukaburu engaŋma.
\p 
\v 25 Mu obo, linyaã mpya ya \qt nswe mbwuru mu be akalyele engaŋma kundaa nganda a nde\qt*, mu kuulu bihi-a-be lili binama bibi nyuru mõ.
\v 26 Mu matala ma liikabagha be nkehe, \qt ka likasa masumu o. Tala linyaã odzyama ŋaala be lili nkini ya nkehe\qt*.
\v 27 Ka likagwa mpeene kundaa dyabulu o.
\v 28 Muturu anyaã ofirikaturu. Lo nde akasa mpini mu osala mu myaã mi nde esala ki ebwe, mpaala nde abagha ki aagwa kundaa wu aakeghele.
\v 29 Ndagha si mõ yi mbi yinyaã opala mu miŋma mi be. Lo kala ti yo yipala, lo yikala yimbwe, yi aatwu, ya yi aagwa bwehe kundaa ba baagyughu yo.
\v 30 Ka likagwa Mufulu a Ngili a Nzaami nyiĩ o, mu kuulu mu nde bási be elyimi mu etsughu ki akala ookwulu be Nzaami.
\v 31 Limaha ŋa kara be nkala, kakaba, nkehe, kyele, bitughu, ya mandagha mwohono ma mabi.
\v 32 Liikakala baara ba babwe ya banga a mikolo nyiĩ be a be, liikasa be a be kolokolo, ti bwunu a bu ósi be Nzaami kolokolo mu Kriste.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Be lifaana okanama bwunu a bu oli Nzaami, ti anga baana baba mukolo,
\v 2 ya liikakala mu dzyi ti bwunu a bu ódzyi bihi-a-be Kriste. Nde ágwi nyuru a nde kundaa Nzaami ti anga ekaba ya mukaba wu otsughu mu nkooro a bihi-a-be, ti anga mananaase mama mpihi yi mbwe.
\p 
\v 3 Ti anga bu ofaana kundaa baba ngili, banyaã ofirikataŋana ŋa kara li be enkwunu, mandagha mama osuŋumu mama mawa-mawa, ntono a nzi.
\v 4 Mbiili yi budzwa, mbiili yi buwulu bwunu we yi mbi ka yifaana ŋa kara li be o. Lo be lifaana okabvurulu matuono.
\v 5 Mu kuulu, ligyighili osoolo ti: Mbwuru si mumõ mu banga-a-enkwunu, baba suŋumu, banga a ntono a nzi (ekye me efaana kii osamana ba nzaami baba mpya), ka babagha pfa mu Emfumu e Kriste ya kii Nzaami o.
\s1 Mu nsi-nkulu mpyibi yi a laŋa-laŋa, mu matala ma ayi otsyeme
\p 
\v 6 Mbwuru anyaã opfiri be mu mbiili yi mukaŋana. Mu kuulu mu nkooro yo nkehe a Nzaami yiigya ŋa yulu a ba baakatemene a Nde ngangala.
\v 7 Ka likala a mfwunu mõ ya bo o.
\v 8 Mu kuulu, mu nsi-nkulu be líili mpyibi yi a laŋa-laŋa, lo mu matala ma be lili otsyeme mu Mfumu. Liikakala ti anga baana baba otsyeme.
\v 9 Mu kuulu, mimburu mi otsyeme me bubwe, bunsumu, engaŋma.
\v 10 Ligyahaba likeene mandagha ma maakagwa Mfumu esee,
\v 11 ya ka likakala bumõ mu bigyighili bi bigwene a mupfunu bibi mpyibi o. Lo liikafwunu bye.
\v 12 Mu kuulu, mandagha ma ookagyighili baara babo mu ensweghe mali mama budzwa mu obili mu mo.
\v 13 Lo bu bafwunu mandagha mamo, mo mamoŋono ŋa otsyeme bu mali mo.
\v 14 Mu kuulu mandagha mwohono maala ayi ma maamoŋono mo mali otsyeme. Mu obo baakalyele ti:
\q1 Sighili, we wuli ensama,
\q1 temene ŋa kara li ba bápki,
\q1 ya Kriste sa atwulu we kunsa otsyeme.
\p 
\v 15 Liikasa mayele mu nzya-nzyara a be: Ka likakala ti anga biwulu o, lo liikakala ti anga banga-a-munzeele,
\v 16 Lisalala matala mukuulu bitsughu bili bibi.
\v 17 Mu obo, ka likala baara ba bagwene a mayele o, lo libaghala waa li Mfumu bunu lili.
\p 
\v 18 Ka likakolo bviini o, mo maakabiri ku odzimini, lo likala ba bálwulu mu Mufulu.
\v 19 Liikagwa be a be mpama mu bikwumu, bikwumu bibi nsia ya bikwumu bi ógwi Mufulu, likagyimi ya likagwa Mfumu nsia mu mukolo a be ndehene.
\v 20 Mu matala mwohono, mu mandagha mwohono, likabvuhulu matuono kundaa munde wu li Nzaami Taara mu nkwumu a Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste.
\s1 Balumu ya bakala
\p 
\v 21 Be ba likagwa Kriste budziri, likakihi litumu li babamõ be a be.
\v 22 Bakaha, liikakihi litumu li balumu ba be ti anga bu liikakihi be litumu li Mfumu.
\v 23 Mu kuulu baghala li mfumu a mukaha, ti anga bu oli Kriste mfumu a Libwunu, li lili nyuru a nde, yi ali nde mubvwuhu.
\v 24 Lo, bwunu a bu ookakihi Libwunu litumu li Kriste, nyaã bakaha si bakakihi litumu li balumu ba bo mu mandagha mwohono.
\p 
\v 25 Balumu, liikadzyi bakala ba be ti anga bu ódzyi Kriste Libwunu ya nde ndeme ágwi nyuru a nde mu nkooro a lo.
\v 26 Obo nde ádzyi osa lo lili ngili bu atsehebe lo mu madza ma maakaswagha ya mu Ndagha,
\v 27 mpaala nde asuo ŋa nkulu a ndeme libwunu li libwe, li ligwene a mpiri, ngu okala mikara, ngu okala elogho ki ebi, lo likala libwunu li lingili ya li ligwene a epfwumu.
\v 28 Bwunu obo si balumu bafaana odzyi bakala ba bo, ti anga manyuru a bomo. Munde wu aakadzyi mukala a nde, nde dzyi nyuru a ndeme.
\p 
\v 29 Mbwuru nkini ka ámaabele nyuru a ndeme o, lo nde aakabuŋunu yo ya aakasa yo bunkere ti anga bu ookasa Kriste mu libwunu,
\v 30 mu kuulu bihi-a-be lili binama bi nyuru a nde.
\v 31 \qt Me mu obo baghala sa asihi taara ya ngughu a nde, sa anabara ya mukala a nde, ya bansa buolo sa bakala nyuru mõ \qt*\f + \fr 5.31 \ft Eba 2.24.\f*.
\v 32 Mamo mali mansweghe ma manene. Me, me ndyele ti mo matala Kriste ya Libwunu li Nzaami.
\v 33 Ngu mu obo, nyaã mumõ-mumõ mu be adzyi mukala a nde ti anga ndeme, ya mukala agwa mulumu a nde budziri.
\c 6
\s1 Baana ya biburu
\p 
\v 1 Baana, liikakihi litumu li biburu bi be, mu kuulu, obo oli bunsumu mu Mfumu.
\v 2 \qt Gwa taara ya ngughu a we budziri\qt*, munde me mukyene wu a nsomo wu li ya misiini:
\v 3 \qt mpaala we kala a esee ya we laama ŋa nsie \qt*.
\p 
\v 4 Be bataara, ka likagwa baana ba be nkehe o, lo liikakwuhu bo kunsa maluo ya mu bigyehe bi Mfumu.
\s1 Bankana ya bamfumu
\p 
\v 5 Bankana, liikasa bintamana kundaa bamfumu ba be baba ŋa nsie kunsa nzalamweẽ ya oteghere, mu mukolo wu bunya-nyaã, ti anga be ba lili mu okasa bintamana kundaa Kriste.
\v 6 Ka likasa obo yini a ŋa mihi mi bo o, ti anga mu omoŋono bubwe kundaa baara, lo likakihi litumu ti anga bankana ba Kriste ba baakagyighili waa li Nzaami mu mukolo mumõ.
\v 7 Liikasalala bo mu mukolo mumõ ti anga be lili mu okasalala Mfumu, lo ka ti anga ba bali mu okasalala baara o,
\v 8 bu lisoolo ti, nswe mbwuru, ngu ali nkana bwunu we mbwuru wu bunya-nyaã, ndeme sa abagha mufuru kundaa Mfumu mu mandagha ma mabwe ma aakagyighili nde.
\p 
\v 9 Kundaa be bamfumu, liikasa bwunu obo si kundaa bankana ba be. Linyaã miŋaana, bu lisoolo Mfumu a bo ya wu a ndaa be li mu mayulu, ya nde ka li a munsuolo a bidzili o.
\s1 Bidzwana bi ookagwa Nzaami
\p 
\v 10 Mu omana, libagha mpini mu Mfumu, mu litumu li lileene li nde lwohono.
\v 11 Lilaha bidzwana bi Nzaami byehene mpaala be lileene otemene ŋa nkulu a bigyighili bi dyabulu bibi emfiri-a-mpya.
\v 12 Mu kuulu, ekyini ki lili a kye, ka eli kii odzwana mu musunu ya makili o, lo kii odzwana a bimpu, bamfumu ya lileene bi nsie yi a mpyibi yi a laŋa-laŋa yi, ekyini kii odzwana a lileene li mifulu mi mibi mi mili ku yulu, ŋa kara li mayulu ya nsie.
\v 13 Mu obo, ligwolo bidzwana bi Nzaami byehene, mpaala be likala a mpini mu etsughu ki ebi ya bu limana ogyighili mandagha mwohono, be litemene bubwe.
\v 14 Mu obo, ligyighili otemene! Lilaha engaŋma ti anga muswele mu bala, ya lilaha bunsumu ti anga enkuru kii mu bisyeẽ ki eekakyi butulu.
\v 15 Lilaha ti anga bikoghoro mu myili mi be mana maa otsala Nsia yi Mbwe yi edzuunu.
\v 16 Mu matala mwohono, ligwolo kana ti anga likubu, mu lo be lileene odzihibi magyo ma mbaa mama Wu Mubi.
\v 17 Ligwolo si obvwughu ti anga mpu yi esyeẽ ya Ndagha a Nzaami ti anga lipee lili Mufulu.
\p 
\v 18 Mu libaha li Mufulu, liikasamana mu Mufulu mu nswe matala mu nsa-nsamana yi mawa-mawa ya yi a opele. Mu obo likahala mihi ya mu nswe matala lisa mukama mu okapele Nzaami mu nkooro a baba ngili bwohono.
\v 19 Liikasamana mu nkooro a mehe si, mpaala Nzaami agwa me ndagha yi olyele mu matala ma akala aandzubulu me muŋma mu otsala mu kana nsia a mansweghe ma Nsia yi Mbwe.
\v 20 Mu nkooro a ndagha oyo me ndi embala kii Nsia yi Mbwe, wu bákuru misyi mimi bisyeẽ. Mu obo liikasamana mpaala me kambili ya kana mu Nsia yi Mbwe bwunu a bu mfaana me obili mu yo.
\s1 Mamboro mama masini
\p 
\v 21 Tisyike sa agwa be mansia mwohono, mpaala behe si lisoolo mandagha ma matala me ya ma ndi mu okagyighili me. Nde li ndughu mu kana wu mukolo, musala a Mfumu wu bakughu osa kana mu nde.
\v 22 Me ngweghe be nde mu mpere mpaala be lisoolo mandagha ma matala bihi, ya mpaala nde agwa be bukyini.
\p 
\v 23 Nyaã edzuunu, dzyi ya kana bi bifi kundaa Nzaami Taara, ya kundaa Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste bikala ya bandughu mu kana!
\v 24 Nyaã bwehe bukala ya babo bwohono ba baakadzyi Mfumu a bihi Yiisu-Kriste mu dzyi li liigwene okabyi!
